{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require GP\u2019s to complete health assessment forms for voluntary roles for free.",
        "additional_details": "My GP surgery wants to charge me \u00a340 to complete the form, most GP\u2019s also have this charging policy in place. At a time of Covid-19 the ambulance service is even more stretched the it was prior to Covid. If you have willing volunteers to help reduce pressure and help care and save lives, why should we be penalised? The costs are not refunded by the ambulance service, and aswell as time we now must give our hard earned cash to volunteer.",
        "background": "I have recently applied and been given an offer of becoming a community first responder (attending 999 calls on behalf of the ambulance service) this role is voluntary. GP\u2019s must sign a form to say your in good health to carry out the role, however most GP\u2019 charge for this around (\u00a340)",
